{"tid":1802534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[智能抗爭] 一人一個抗爭謬誤","createTime":"2019-12-29T14:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T14:52:23.000Z","uid":185628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3034d33086095fc22c0d59ae59dde2a9fad2e78f","tid":1802534,"uid":185628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T14:03:49.000Z","msg":"1. 勇武一定有用過和理非<br />\n無可否認勇武對撤回惡法有重大貢獻, 但係並非所有勇武行動都係值得做<br />\n判斷一個抗爭活動值唔值得做嘅三個準則:<br />\na) 無其他活動更能打擊敵人(物理，精神，物資上)<br />\nb) 對自身安全無風險, 但又能夠打擊敵人<br />\nc) 唔檢討就吹雞叫人行動<br />\n<br />\n2. 唔快d行動就會丟淡件事<br />\n要人唔好忘記，左膠搞咁多年平反六四個模式已經好成功啦<br />\n勇武行動根本唔係為左提醒"},{"pid":"32c42e1a33421f2bca4f0529647c7bd510e50b80","tid":1802534,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T14:04:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德國聯署有三份  呢家<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有一份未達標</span><br />\n而且差好遠呀<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 1xxxx/50000</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK96joMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=696c3cbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"632b7447017276b7bf5a9134bfaebd0fe1ccf14d","tid":1802534,"uid":274141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T14:52:23.000Z","msg":"除夕夜唔好再叫「10，9，光，復，香，港，時，代，革，命」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1802587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1802587</a>"}]}